{"tid":497831,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"$3000教補習羽毛球教練（後記）","createTime":"2017-12-13T07:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T16:29:07.000Z","uid":104836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d786925ea1fd0d8f615a6d4fe2c7f4d191c5555","tid":497831,"uid":104836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"承上題<br />\n上次講到我老母搵左個羽毛球教練番黎教細佬妹讀書<br />\n我心諗傻很左呀？<br />\n但然後呢期佢地啲測驗呀 默書呀戈啲成績出左黎<br />\n又真係有明顯進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我怪好錯左佢？雖然真係好很貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過老母話佢淨係$3000蚊教一堂<br />\n然後就唔會再有下一堂 淨係會肯比佢地再message問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢教嘅係咪即係平時出面啲人講嘅記憶大法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9333f8a6a424a3944afa71095b3ba08060fc0e49","tid":497831,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"羽毛球教練一樣可以有大學學歷，不過3000一堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203e4459133d0cdd4c58ef6d46897af42ff47938","tid":497831,"uid":104836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羽毛球教練一樣可以有大學學歷，不過3000一堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似話真係讀過大學嘅<br />\n但邊間我就真係唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463b054e18eff5ad2ca4676b30ed73e87b14a3bf","tid":497831,"uid":41461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"你細佬妹係小學生？<br />\n<br />\n咁求其喺街執個後生仔 都教得掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2187138f979033f910b8fc6ad57469fbdfdde60","tid":497831,"uid":104836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20